    <h1>THE BLENDED I.R.I.S PROJECT</h1>
    <!--    <img src="../Gallery/Portfolio Image/Port1.jpg" alt="Audience" />-->

    <p>Welcome <strong>To A Blended Environment</strong>.</p>

    <p>
      Sorlato’s Café was one of my attempts at creating another social space within Roblox. It serves as a realm connected to my game and was built as a gift for a friend I met during my first year of college. We spent time hanging out in Roblox, and this café became a tribute to that friendship. Located on an island in the middle of the void, it features a small, cozy space for people to chat and relax. Originally, the island was larger, but due to lag issues it was drastically reduced. The café includes a teleport pad accessible only to selected members, which leads to a private talking area. This game serves as a lore builder that establishes worlds beyond my current projects while blending natural elements with modern design.
    </p>

